# c-yesterday-support.md

Source of truth for `/c-yesterday`. Cumulative chat ledger from 2026-04-23 onward, append-only. Mirrors `/c-netlify-database` 4-col look — `🌐🌐` flag = chat shipped to a Netlify deploy (sourced from `## NETLIFY LINKS`, populated by `/c-netlify-yesterday-sync`).

The skill is a dumb pipe — this file is the formatter. Default fire prints `## CACHED LEDGER` verbatim with zero parsing.

